    Createable
    Defines a creatable object behavior.
    LevelLoader
    this interface can load level in any way you want, without a need to change Level class.
    LevelLoaderCreator
    Define a level loader creator behavior.
    LevelSaver
    Defines a level saver behavior.
    LevelSaverCreator
    Defines a level saver creator behavior.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MyObjectLevelLoader
    Loads a level using the object input stream with any InputStream given.
    MyObjectLevelSaver
    Saves a level using the object output stream with any OutputStream given.
    MyTextLevelLoader
    Loads level from a text file from any InputStream.
    MyTextLevelSaver
    Saves a level to a text file through any OutputStream.
    MyXMLLevelLoader
    Loads a level from an XML file through any InputStream.
    MyXMLLevelSaver
    Saves a level to an XML file through any OutputStream.

    ObjectLevelSaverCreator

    TextLevelLoaderCreator

    TextLevelSaverCreator

    XMLLevelSaverCreator
    Creates a XML level saver.
